Puppet module: mcollective

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages mcollective software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include mcollective              # Install and run mcollective with standard configurations.
include mcollective::disable     # Disable mcollective service.
include mcollective::disableboot # Disable mcollective service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include mcollective::absent      # Remove mcollective package.

DEPENDENCIES:
